net.milkbowl.vault2.economy

Class EconomyResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.milkbowl.vault2.economy.EconomyResponse

  • public class EconomyResponse
extends Object
    Indicates a typical Return for an Economy method. It includes a EconomyResponse.ResponseType indicating whether the plugin currently being used for Economy actually allows the method, or if the operation was a success or failure.
